    <defName>MantisBSBlue01</defName>
    <title>Malfunction Defense System</title>
    <titleShort>whitehat</titleShort>
	<baseDescription>While wandering in the Slug Home Nebula, NAME found a Slug vessel broadcasting the distress signal and contacted them. "Ah, yesss, we are having problems with our oxygen generation unit. Perhaps your crew can assist in repairsss?". Once on board, it became clear that nothing was wrong with their O2 system. Almost expecting this, NAME calmly responded to the trap. Once a couple of the Slugs had been spread across the walls of their ship, the rest surrendered.</baseDescription>
