	<AlienRace.BackstoryDef>
    <defName>MantisBSBlue02</defName>
    <title>met legendary KazaaakplethKilik</title>
    <titleShort>Diplomat</titleShort>
	<baseDescription>NAME crossed paths with a Mantis ship that looked to have had dozens of layers of armor-plating added over what must have been a hundred year career. Its captain was legendary thief KazaaakplethKilik. NAME's crew looked frightened. NAME stepped forward. HE and KazaaakplethKilik performed a weird kind of alien haka, while the crew was charging the battle systems. After destroying KazaaakplethKilik ship, HE quickly teleported and brought him back. HIS haste had paid off and HE registered KazaaakplethKilik into the Clonebay's database. After he passes away he is quickly reconstructed on board your ship. When his senses return he says, "I never thought I would see this day, but... I am willing to devote myself and my ships to your cause."</baseDescription>
    <slot>Adulthood</slot>
