	<AlienRace.BackstoryDef>
		<defName>MantisBSBlue03</defName>
		<title>Confused</title>
		<titleShort>confused</titleShort>
		<baseDescription>While wandering in the Engi Homeworlds, a spaceship you received a hail from a nearby civilian Engi vessel. Their Captain appeared on screen: "Strange bug. Can you assist in debugging?" "Found malfunctioning Mantis. Believes it is human. Will receive input only from human. Danger Evaluation: Extremely High. Provide assistance." The crew sent his human crew member and HE was grateful to see 'another human', and introduced himself as NAME. HE explained HE was from a nearby human colony and would appreciate being returned there. The colony is a mining operation that specializes in FTL fuel. Robert's family, the head engineers, are excited to see him, and very grateful for his return. Apparently HE ran away to 'join the Federation' like his older brother, but was never accepted onto a ship. The crew offered HIM a position. HE graciously accepted, having always wanted to serve in the Federation.</baseDescription>
		<slot>Adulthood</slot>
		
