    <defName>MantisBSBlue04</defName>
    <title>Mantis distress call</title>
    <titleShort>By the sword</titleShort>
	<baseDescription>While visiting Mantis Homeworlds, a crew came across an Engi wreck with one life-sign aboard; it turned out to be the sole survivor of the Mantis boarding party that wiped out the ship's crew. HE's in no state to fight and HE's brought aboard. The crew sent its mantis member to negotiate. After a short time alone with the commando, the crew was told HE wished to join the crew. Although the crew was surprised at NAME willingness to swap allegiances, it trusted its crewmember judgement about him.
.</baseDescription>
